# Styling Guidelines

## Tailwind CSS
- Use [cn()](mdc:src/lib/utils.ts) for conditional classes
- class-variance-authority for component variants
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Support light/dark themes

## Component Patterns
- Build reusable UI in [components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui/)
- Consistent design tokens (spacing, colors, typography)
- Proper focus states and accessibility
- Loading/disabled states for interactive elements

## PWA Considerations
- Minimum 44px touch targets
- Optimize for mobile viewports
- App-like navigation patterns
- Offline state styling

## Architecture
- Minimal custom CSS in [globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)
- Avoid inline styles
- Use semantic color naming (primary, secondary, accent)
- Ensure sufficient contrast ratios

